N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 495-1.12 - Treatment of Confidential Information

State Regulations

Submission of records pursuant to this Part containing
trade secrets, confidential commercial information, or critical infrastructure
information will be handled pursuant to section
616.7
of this
